---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { SITE } from "../consts";
---

<BaseLayout
  title={`AC Repair Tupelo, MS | ${SITE.name}`}
  description="Need to fix air conditioner issues in Tupelo? Learn common causes, early checks, and when to request local AC repair help."
  canonical={`${SITE.url}/ac-repair-tupelo/`}
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container surface service">
      <p class="eyebrow">AC Repair Tupelo</p>
      <h1>Fix Air Conditioner Problems in Tupelo, MS</h1>
      <p>
        If your AC is blowing warm air, short cycling, or struggling during humid afternoons, you may need targeted AC
        repair in Tupelo. Common issues include clogged filters, thermostat mismatch, low refrigerant, and dirty
        condenser coils.
      </p>
      <h2>What to check first</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Replace a dirty return-air filter.</li>
        <li>Confirm the thermostat is set to cool and fan is auto.</li>
        <li>Make sure supply vents are open and not blocked.</li>
        <li>Inspect your outdoor unit for debris buildup.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        If the issue continues, request service so a local pro can diagnose safely. For ongoing tune-ups, see
        <a href="/hvac-maintenance-tupelo/"> HVAC maintenance in Tupelo</a>.
      </p>
      <div class="cta-row">
        <a class="button primary" href="/#request-service">Request Service</a>
        <a class="button secondary" href="/contact/">Get a Quote</a>
        <a class="button secondary" href="/tupelo-hvac-guide/">Read the Tupelo HVAC Guide</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .service {
    padding: var(--space-6);
    max-width: 900px;
  }
  .cta-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
</style>
